=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_XFade2_ex1 ===

DESCRIPTION: A bright pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 441 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, and filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: bright
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: moderate
  spectral_flux_normalized: stable
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 441.2715
  harmonic_decay_rate: -6.2300
  harmonic_regularity: 0.7848
  pitch_clarity: 405.2688
  inharmonicity: 0.0000
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -7.9132
  resonance_freq: 430.6641

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
